{"tid":1036652,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[懷念Stan Lee爺爺] Captain Marvel 討論區（6/3/19上映）","createTime":"2019-02-25T11:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T16:56:20.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d6197cbdbd37b79c84933cb36e5857b82e8952cb","tid":1036652,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPPNoKf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPPNoKf.jpg&h=5117007c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GTbXFQHgsHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGTbXFQHgsHo&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8ScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=3dada222\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GTbXFQHgsHo</a><br />\n預告1<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6C0tKt-8Pl8&amp;t=14s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6C0tKt-8Pl8%26t%3D14s&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8ScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=bfd4eebb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6C0tKt-8Pl8&amp;t=14s</a><br />\n預告2<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介：<br />\n本是美國空軍飛行員的卡蘿丹佛斯(貝兒娜森 飾演)，因為一次意外之下失去記憶並流落外星，由「詭族」獲得超強能力她因為追擊異星敵人再次回到地球，並認識了「費特工」(森姆積遜 飾演)，協助其對抗強敵之時，更逐漸揭開其真正身份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/captain-marvel-poster-brie-larson1-456x676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fcaptain-marvel-poster-brie-larson1-456x676.jpg&h=38752b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/captain-marvel-poster-jude-law-456x676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fcaptain-marvel-poster-jude-law-456x676.jpg&h=c750bebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/captain-marvel-poster-djimon-hounsou-456x676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fcaptain-marvel-poster-djimon-hounsou-456x676.jpg&h=495abfcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/captain-marvel-poster-gemma-chan-456x676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fcaptain-marvel-poster-gemma-chan-456x676.jpg&h=f6c998fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/captain-marvel-poster-lashana-lynch-456x676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fcaptain-marvel-poster-lashana-lynch-456x676.jpg&h=8d2a418f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/captain-marvel-poster-annette-bening-456x676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fcaptain-marvel-poster-annette-bening-456x676.jpg&h=df10f438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/captain-marvel-poster-ben-mendelsohn-456x676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fcaptain-marvel-poster-ben-mendelsohn-456x676.jpg&h=183bda1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/captain-marvel-poster-samuel-l-jackson-456x676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.collider.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fcaptain-marvel-poster-samuel-l-jackson-456x676.jpg&h=d5dbb13f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.collider.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/captain-marvel-poster-clark-gregg-456x676.jpg\" da